    "description": "Renders items as clickable cards suitable for lists and grids. Shows title, truncated preview text, type metadata, and compact tag pills.\n\n## Features\n\n- Title from `item.name`\n- 2-line preview from `item.content.description`\n- Type name and compact tag pills in footer\n- Hover animation (subtle slide and border color)\n- Click opens item via `open-item!` (supports Ctrl/Cmd+Click for new tab, Alt+Click for root)\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- Search results\n- Tag browser listings\n- Compact item indexes",
