    "code": "(defn render [item api]\n  (def it item)\n  (def name (or (:name it) (subs (:id it) 0 8)))\n  (def raw-desc (or (get-in it [:content :description]) \"\"))\n  (def preview (if (string? raw-desc) raw-desc (extract-text raw-desc)))\n  (def type-item (get-item (:type it)))\n  (def tag-ids (or (get-in it [:content :tags]) []))\n  [\n    :div.compact-card\n    {\n      :style \"padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--border-radius); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;\"\n      :on-click (fn [e] (open-item! e (:id it)))}\n    [\n      :div\n      {:style \"font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 6px; overflow: hidden;\"}\n      name]\n    (when (seq preview)\n      [\n        :div\n        {\n          :style \"font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 6px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\"}\n        (if (> (count preview) 200) (subs preview 0 200) preview)])\n    [\n      :div\n      {\n        :style \"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-border-dark);\"}\n      [:span (str \"Type: \" (:name type-item))]\n      (for [tag-id tag-ids]\n        (let [\n                tag\n                (get-item tag-id)\n                color\n                (or (get-in tag [:content :color]) \"var(--color-primary)\")\n                tag-name\n                (or (get-in tag [:content :name]) (:name tag) (subs (:id tag) 0 8))]\n          [\n            :span\n            {\n              :style (str\n                \"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.625rem; cursor: pointer; color: \"\n                color\n                \"; background: \"\n                color\n                \"20; border: 1px solid \"\n                color\n                \"40;\")\n              :on-click (fn [e] (open-item! e (:id tag)))}\n            [\n              :span\n              {\n                :style (str \"width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; background: \" color \";\")}]\n            [:span tag-name]]))]])\n",
